00:00:03.250 --> 00:00:06.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I have a teacher,
and it's Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:09.380 --> 00:00:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SERIE] You pass.
-[yawning]</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] Next.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Denken the Imperial Mage.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:49.030 --> 00:01:50.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know all about you.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am honored to hear it,
Mistress Serie.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] A self-made man who got
his start in the military,</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:58.330 --> 00:02:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then rose to be
the most influential mage</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:00.580 --> 00:02:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in all the northern lands.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:02.790 --> 00:02:05.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the subject
of many an inspiring tale.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:06.290 --> 00:02:07.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To tell you the truth,</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wish that I'd met you
when you were still young.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still full of energy
and ambition,</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your passion burning bright.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water splattering]</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:22.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no interest
in a great flame's cinders.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least that's
what I believed.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And do you believe
differently, now?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:33.740 --> 00:02:34.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:35.410 --> 00:02:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you first walked in,</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:36.910 --> 00:02:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you considered how
you would fight me.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] I did,
but only for a moment.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I quickly abandoned that idea.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:46.750 --> 00:02:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fire remains.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so, you pass.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:50.710 --> 00:02:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most people
are too afraid to fight me</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:52.510 --> 00:02:53.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even in their heads.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:55.380 --> 00:02:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:56.470 --> 00:03:01.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:01.810 --> 00:03:03.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've passed the test.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:03.310 --> 00:03:06.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm? I'm pretty sure
interviews require words.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:07.350 --> 00:03:09.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] Were you hoping
for conversation?</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:10.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:10.980 --> 00:03:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know when to quit.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:12.940 --> 00:03:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:17.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Young man, is this a joke?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:20.370 --> 00:03:21.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pardon?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:21.660 --> 00:03:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're taking
the first-class mage exam.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:25.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really couldn't be
bothered to set foot</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:25.870 --> 00:03:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the testing grounds?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:29.090 --> 00:03:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As you can see,</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the real me has made
an appearance</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:35.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in case that is a requirement
for passing.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:37.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not so easily deceived.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:40.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your actual body
never left your hometown.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:42.260 --> 00:03:44.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you're enjoying
that cup of tea.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:44.470 --> 00:03:48.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:49.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How impressive.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:52.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even Ubel realized it.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have tremendous nerve.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:56.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You pass.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:56.650 --> 00:03:57.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:57.860 --> 00:03:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:59.950 --> 00:04:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] You're Wirbel,</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:00.870 --> 00:04:02.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>captain of
the Northern Magic Corps.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of all the second-class mages
I know,</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:07.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you are by far
the most skilled in combat.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:07.830 --> 00:04:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:10.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] In a single look,</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:10.670 --> 00:04:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you realized a battle
with me would be pointless.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:13.460 --> 00:04:16.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that wasn't a judgment
made out of fear.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I were the type
to pick fights I can't win,</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:19.050 --> 00:04:21.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have even
made it to second class.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:22.140 --> 00:04:23.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a good point.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:25.390 --> 00:04:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's your favorite spell?</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:28.060 --> 00:04:30.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] Spells aren't to be
liked or disliked.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:30.810 --> 00:04:32.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic's a tool for killing.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:33.110 --> 00:04:34.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:34.610 --> 00:04:35.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have passed.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:36.110 --> 00:04:37.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:41.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:41.620 --> 00:04:42.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did you think
when you saw me?</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:44.620 --> 00:04:45.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[METHODE] Well, um,</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:47.620 --> 00:04:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were very small
and very adorable?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:52.790 --> 00:04:54.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] This year's test-takers</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:54.170 --> 00:04:56.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are a different breed
all together.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:57.050 --> 00:04:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] You pass.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:00.050 --> 00:05:01.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:05.140 --> 00:05:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sense.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:07.180 --> 00:05:08.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My apologies.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:09.270 --> 00:05:11.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It does seem
we have a bumper crop.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:15.820 --> 00:05:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SCHARF] I failed.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:18.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Always next time, champ.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND] Stop following
me around.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:21.530 --> 00:05:22.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A whole three years, huh?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:24.570 --> 00:05:26.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I passed the test,
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:27.450 --> 00:05:28.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excellent job.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:34.460 --> 00:05:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who knows how far
I would've made it</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:36.090 --> 00:05:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without you and your protege.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to you,
I can finally visit</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:40.550 --> 00:05:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a certain grave up north.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:44.010 --> 00:05:45.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Come on, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:55.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You gotta pick something.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:58.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:07.240 --> 00:06:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I think I'd like--
[LAUFEN] I want these, Grandpa.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:10.410 --> 00:06:11.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:14.870 --> 00:06:19.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:19.130 --> 00:06:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eat up, everyone.
Don't be shy.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:21.670 --> 00:06:23.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I was a lad,
I never got to indulge</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in sweet treats like these.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:27.260 --> 00:06:28.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you very much, sir.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:33.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:33.770 --> 00:06:35.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Am I missing something?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:35.770 --> 00:06:39.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:39.610 --> 00:06:41.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have a few, young man.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:41.900 --> 00:06:42.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Appreciate it, old-timer.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:45.700 --> 00:06:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:53.210 --> 00:06:54.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Who's he?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's Mister Denken.
He's an Imperial Mage.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:57.830 --> 00:07:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Well, that sounds
awfully fancy.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:03.670 --> 00:07:04.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Huh.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:05.430 --> 00:07:07.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean
the old timer's a noble?</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:07.930 --> 00:07:08.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oopsie.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:09.010 --> 00:07:11.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry for speaking
to you so casually.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:11.930 --> 00:07:13.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry yourself.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:13.180 --> 00:07:16.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came to this city as a mage
just like any other.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:16.650 --> 00:07:18.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Sure, but you shouldn't
feel obliged</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:18.810 --> 00:07:20.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to treat a stranger like me.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:21.110 --> 00:07:23.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please. I have no
better use for my money.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on,
that can't be the truth.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's right. No family?</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:28.870 --> 00:07:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Hm?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't blessed with
children or grandchildren.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:33.830 --> 00:07:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My wife passed away
when I was in my mid-twenties.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:42.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The poor girl was sickly
from the day we met.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her father
was a frontier noble</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:44.630 --> 00:07:46.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Northern Plateau
and had been defeated</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:46.590 --> 00:07:47.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a political dispute.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:49.470 --> 00:07:51.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back in those days,
wealth and influence</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:51.430 --> 00:07:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were two things
I desperately lacked.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:53.810 --> 00:07:56.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They also seemed
to be the only mechanisms</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:56.640 --> 00:07:58.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by which I could save her.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:59.730 --> 00:08:01.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Soon, Serie established</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:01.190 --> 00:08:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Continental
Magic Association</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and began offering
the privilege.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:05.030 --> 00:08:06.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it was too late.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:06.650 --> 00:08:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My wife had just passed.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:08.910 --> 00:08:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had never felt
so powerless in my life.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:16.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now I have
all the power in the world.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:19.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only I could have been
for my beloved then</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:19.210 --> 00:08:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who I have become today.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:22.290 --> 00:08:23.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[DENKEN] Fern.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my life,
magic was reduced to a tool</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:26.420 --> 00:08:28.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for resolving
political disputes.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:29.390 --> 00:08:31.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is something I'd like
you to tell your master.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:34.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I had long forgotten
how joyful magic can be,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:37.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she gave me
a firm reminder.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:40.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've admired Frieren's deeds
in the party of heroes</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:41.020 --> 00:08:42.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since I was a boy.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:42.190 --> 00:08:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I credit her
with my becoming a mage.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:45.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:47.450 --> 00:08:49.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should tell her
that yourself.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:49.570 --> 00:08:51.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain she would
be happy to hear it.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:54.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps you're right.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:55.580 --> 00:08:56.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do that.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:03.670 --> 00:09:06.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:09.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The magical city of AuBerst
did not disappoint.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:11.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I found some
top-notch grimoires.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:13.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clattering]
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] Allow me.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want them
in the basket, right?</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:22.650 --> 00:09:24.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:27.860 --> 00:09:29.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You would ignore the poor lady?</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Helping her did cross
my mind for a moment.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:32.860 --> 00:09:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just a moment, huh?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised at you.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:36.990 --> 00:09:38.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were a member
of Himmel's party.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:39.370 --> 00:09:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think there's a certain way
I should act, yes?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:44.290 --> 00:09:46.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your actions have been
more surprising than mine.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:49.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard that you tried
to kill Fern's party</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:49.710 --> 00:09:50.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the first test.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:51.340 --> 00:09:52.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern was quite upset.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:53.260 --> 00:09:55.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said you'd kick a puppy
if it was in your way.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:56.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:56.930 --> 00:09:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many folks would agree.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:59.350 --> 00:10:00.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I did was threaten them.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:02.310 --> 00:10:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though looking back, if I
had taken one of those lives,</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:05.100 --> 00:10:07.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might've been doing
the world a favor.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:10.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no one I wouldn't kill</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:10.650 --> 00:10:12.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to protect my village
and the people in it.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:16.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The whole reason
I'm here is the privilege.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:16.620 --> 00:10:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to get my hands on
the most powerful spell I can.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:19.830 --> 00:10:20.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The demons already thought</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:22.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was a force
to be reckoned with,</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:22.660 --> 00:10:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but they haven't seen
anything yet.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:25.670 --> 00:10:28.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I protect, but I also try
to help when I can.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:29.090 --> 00:10:30.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any place and anybody.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:33.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goal is to lighten the load
of people in need.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:34.090 --> 00:10:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:38.220 --> 00:10:40.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like countless others
born on the northern frontier,</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:42.020 --> 00:10:45.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my childhood was dominated
by tales of Himmel the Hero.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:48.020 --> 00:10:50.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The conquest
of the Thousand-Mirror Tower.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:50.610 --> 00:10:52.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His battles against Bose
the Immortal.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:53.110 --> 00:10:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the Hell Emperor Dragon.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:56.110 --> 00:10:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As a kid, I would sink my teeth</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:57.780 --> 00:11:00.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into every adventure story
that made it my way.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:01.870 --> 00:11:03.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the village elders
were never as interested</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:03.870 --> 00:11:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in those stories
of swords as I was.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:07.630 --> 00:11:09.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'd talk about
how he defeated</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:09.170 --> 00:11:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the monsters that
attacked the village,</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:11.340 --> 00:11:13.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or how he once guarded
some merchant,</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or how he helped
little old ladies</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:16.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>carry their groceries.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:19.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those tales were
nothing significant.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:19.930 --> 00:11:21.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just boring favors.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I thought, anyway.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:24.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But when the elders
shared them,</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:24.980 --> 00:11:26.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>their eyes lit up bright,</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:28.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as thrilled
by these small deeds</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as I was by the great ones.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:32.940 --> 00:11:34.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After Himmel the Hero died</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:36.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the remaining demons
started acting up,</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:37.030 --> 00:11:38.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's when
I finally understood.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:40.070 --> 00:11:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:49.380 --> 00:11:52.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] Sure enough,
the Thousand-Mirror Tower,</b></Default>

c0000224
00:11:52.380 --> 00:11:54.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bose, the Hell Emperor Dragon,</b></Default>

c0000225
00:11:55.130 --> 00:11:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even the Demon King?</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:56.970 --> 00:11:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>None of them meant
as much as home.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:59.970 --> 00:12:01.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And home keeps
your hands too full</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:02.060 --> 00:12:03.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to worry about
that kind of stuff.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:05.310 --> 00:12:08.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thing is, if Himmel the Hero
hadn't visited my village,</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:09.940 --> 00:12:11.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt that my home
would still be around,</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:12.070 --> 00:12:14.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>whether he had
saved the world or not.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:14.900 --> 00:12:17.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.
And all that to say?</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:17.990 --> 00:12:20.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That the small stuff
counts just as much!</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel's less-exciting
adventures</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:22.280 --> 00:12:23.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are what guided me here.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:23.830 --> 00:12:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:26.830 --> 00:12:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] It's really
nothing that complex.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:28.710 --> 00:12:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:31.750 --> 00:12:34.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] Guess I've been
chatting for too long.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:36.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My party's ready
to hit the road,</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:37.260 --> 00:12:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they look impatient.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:41.470 --> 00:12:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:42.800 --> 00:12:44.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Always treasure
the people you meet.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:45.930 --> 00:12:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Death is far from this
lifetime's only goodbye.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:49.190 --> 00:12:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then again,
I don't have to tell you that.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:54.020 --> 00:12:57.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:58.820 --> 00:13:01.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sheep bleating]</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:01.910 --> 00:13:03.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren. If we go one by one,</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:04.080 --> 00:13:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't there some way you could
magic each of us across?</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:07.450 --> 00:13:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Possibly, but then I'd be left
all alone on this side.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:10.960 --> 00:13:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:12.540 --> 00:13:15.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should waste no time
in defeating the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:16.510 --> 00:13:18.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What point is there
in helping people</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:18.130 --> 00:13:20.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in such insignificant ways?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:24.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] They are
insignificant, I suppose.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:26.180 --> 00:13:28.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Deeds like these
will not change lives,</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:29.100 --> 00:13:30.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>let alone the world.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:32.270 --> 00:13:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But people need help,</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:36.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I cannot turn my back
on those right in front of me.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:45.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:48.290 --> 00:13:49.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Don't worry, Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:51.460 --> 00:13:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It turns out the world
was changed after all.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:57.500 --> 00:13:59.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] We're going to be
granted our privileges tonight,</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:02.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and apparently, we're each
allowed to bring guests.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:03.220 --> 00:14:04.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's once in a lifetime.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So we should all go.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:07.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:10.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Goodness,
Mistress Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:10.350 --> 00:14:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't look so excited.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:12.980 --> 00:14:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? But I was told we were
allowed to bring guests.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:17.230 --> 00:14:18.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm terribly sorry, ma'am,</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:18.940 --> 00:14:20.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but Miss Frieren
has been banned.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:20.780 --> 00:14:22.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Serie's orders.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:22.990 --> 00:14:24.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's barred from all
Continental Magic</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:24.950 --> 00:14:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Association facilities
for the next 1000 years.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:14:28.870 --> 00:14:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's quite a steep punishment
when there wasn't a crime.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:14:32.460 --> 00:14:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't be helped.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:36.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've gotten on her bad side,
and that's where I'll stay.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Serie is truly
the world's oldest child.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not as if I came here
of my own accord, anyway.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:45.300 --> 00:14:46.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall wait outside.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:47.050 --> 00:14:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:50.220 --> 00:14:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I may as well give her
some company.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:55.850 --> 00:15:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:04.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bell rings]</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:05.990 --> 00:15:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the evening bell.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:07.910 --> 00:15:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'll be done receiving
their privileges before long.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:10.870 --> 00:15:11.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:12.290 --> 00:15:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a first-class mage now.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:14.670 --> 00:15:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a pinnacle
not even 50 mages</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:16.710 --> 00:15:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the whole world
have reached.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:19.130 --> 00:15:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Young Fern has grown so much.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:28.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt, in this era,</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:28.220 --> 00:15:30.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern will become a mage
even more famous than me.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:33.810 --> 00:15:34.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:35.690 --> 00:15:36.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a good thing.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:38.310 --> 00:15:40.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] I agree.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:41.020 --> 00:15:42.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LERNEN] Miss Frieren.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:15:45.610 --> 00:15:46.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who's he?</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:46.570 --> 00:15:48.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's one
of the Magic Association's men.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:49.280 --> 00:15:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is Lernen,
and I'm a first class-mage.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:52.330 --> 00:15:54.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A longtime student
of Mistress Serie.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:55.540 --> 00:15:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am sorry for the trouble
my mistress has caused you.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:00.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No worries there.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:03.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She has behaved
just as I expected.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:04.920 --> 00:16:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:06.380 --> 00:16:07.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong, Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:10.300 --> 00:16:11.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The way
you're looking at me.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:12.260 --> 00:16:14.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see the fluctuations
in my mana.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:16.180 --> 00:16:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are tremendously skilled,</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:18.190 --> 00:16:20.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but this peaceful era
doesn't suit you, does it?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:20.690 --> 00:16:22.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LERNEN] Not in the slightest.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:22.230 --> 00:16:24.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am an old-fashioned mage</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who knows painfully little
outside the realm of battle.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:29.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Serie
often says the same.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:32.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only I'd been
born in the height</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Demon King's reign,</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:33.700 --> 00:16:35.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my name would've been
written in history</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:35.950 --> 00:16:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>alongside the names of the rest
of you famous heroes.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:39.710 --> 00:16:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:43.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what is it you want
from me, then?</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:45.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Out of all
Mistress Serie's students,</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:45.920 --> 00:16:47.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's only one
remembered today.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:48.090 --> 00:16:49.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her very first apprentice,</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:52.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the legendary
Great Mage Flamme.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:55.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no secret I am soon
to return to dust,</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:55.600 --> 00:16:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and when I die,
so will some proof</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:57.940 --> 00:16:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of my mistress's existence.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:17:00.060 --> 00:17:02.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want her
to be alone in the future.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I'll leave a legacy
to keep her company.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:17:05.820 --> 00:17:08.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Infamy must suffice,
as being the mage</b></Default>

c0000336
00:17:08.150 --> 00:17:09.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who killed
the legendary Frieren</b></Default>

c0000337
00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>won't illicit kind remarks
from generations to come.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:13.070 --> 00:17:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:18.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:21.580 --> 00:17:22.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:30.510 --> 00:17:31.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LERNEN] I request a duel,</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:32.340 --> 00:17:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Miss Frieren.
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:34.180 --> 00:17:35.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I am not
going to fight you.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:36.260 --> 00:17:37.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a waste of time.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a bother.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:40.770 --> 00:17:42.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mages who only know
how to fight</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:44.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are simply horrid
at the softer things.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:46.400 --> 00:17:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's really no need
for history to remember you.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:51.610 --> 00:17:53.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Serie will do
a fine job of that.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:56.080 --> 00:17:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:57.950 --> 00:17:59.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One thing before I go.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:01.000 --> 00:18:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That small field of flowers
was conjured by magic.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:05.540 --> 00:18:07.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, and your point is?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:08.010 --> 00:18:10.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That you used
my master's favorite spell.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:13.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You told me that you
found it foolish and useless.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:14.180 --> 00:18:17.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:17.850 --> 00:18:20.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am not one to mince words.
Flamme was a failure.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:22.180 --> 00:18:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Despite her immense talent,</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:24.350 --> 00:18:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she never reached my heights.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:29.190 --> 00:18:31.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've taken on
many apprentices since,</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:32.740 --> 00:18:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>most of whom
followed a similar,</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:34.490 --> 00:18:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>disappointing trajectory.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:37.870 --> 00:18:39.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The failures that they were?</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:40.330 --> 00:18:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember each and every one.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I always choose
my students on a whim,</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:44.920 --> 00:18:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yet their personalities
and favorite spells</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:47.290 --> 00:18:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are carved into my mind.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As pitiful as most
proved to be,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:54.630 --> 00:18:56.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never regretted
taking them on.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:58.100 --> 00:19:00.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if they didn't become
the legends I foresaw.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:19:02.730 --> 00:19:04.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It's a pity
she can't tell her own students</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:04.900 --> 00:19:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how she truly feels.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:09.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's ever the child
I thought she was.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:14.200 --> 00:19:16.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Mistress Frieren!</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:17.570 --> 00:19:19.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm all done
receiving my privilege.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's be off, then.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:21.950 --> 00:19:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Goodness.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:23.040 --> 00:19:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you get
that wound on your shoulder?</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:25.660 --> 00:19:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that matters now
is getting it healed.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:28.250 --> 00:19:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think there are
any churches open?</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:31.420 --> 00:19:33.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are horrid at
the softer things, aren't we?</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:36.630 --> 00:19:38.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LERNEN] That is true
of the both of us.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:42.520 --> 00:19:43.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[all chuckle]
-Mister Stark!</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:43.890 --> 00:19:45.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What's today's mission?
-[ALL] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:45.770 --> 00:19:46.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Sorry, kiddos.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:46.940 --> 00:19:48.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid
I can't play this time.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:49.270 --> 00:19:50.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Stark!</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:50.270 --> 00:19:51.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How 'bout some breakfast
on the house?</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:51.900 --> 00:19:53.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks, but I already ate.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:53.480 --> 00:19:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark! Would you
like something to drink?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:55.950 --> 00:19:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Sure, thank you.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:58.200 --> 00:20:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The path of the warrior is
a long and treacherous one.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:20:01.740 --> 00:20:03.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Walk it with care.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:04.040 --> 00:20:05.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It's time to say
goodbye to AuBerst.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:12.380 --> 00:20:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:13.670 --> 00:20:15.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People love you
everywhere you go.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:15.840 --> 00:20:16.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think so?</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:18.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:19.180 --> 00:20:21.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What spell did you
end up asking for?</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:23.260 --> 00:20:24.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:25.600 --> 00:20:26.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:28.190 --> 00:20:29.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What, can you not tell?</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:31.150 --> 00:20:33.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your clothes are so clean
they look new.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:34.150 --> 00:20:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffs]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:35.480 --> 00:20:38.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And there's a vaguely
floral smell about them.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:39.030 --> 00:20:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe it.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:42.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a spell that
removes stains</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:42.780 --> 00:20:44.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and cleans clothes
down to the stitch.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:45.080 --> 00:20:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's going to make doing
laundry a breeze.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:47.710 --> 00:20:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Serie is a living grimoire
after all, then.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:51.290 --> 00:20:53.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've won a legendary-level
cleaning spell</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:53.540 --> 00:20:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the era of mythology.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:56.670 --> 00:20:58.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Superb choice, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:58.340 --> 00:20:59.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[excited]</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:59.970 --> 00:21:02.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is no doubt
you're my apprentice.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:02.470 --> 00:21:05.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:05.850 --> 00:21:07.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's for sure.
Not one bit.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:10.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Serie didn't seem</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:10.440 --> 00:21:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>quite as happy
with my selection, though.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:13.060 --> 00:21:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you out of your mind?</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:15.570 --> 00:21:17.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I believe it.
Serves her right.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:21.450 --> 00:21:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] Oh! They're here.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:24.330 --> 00:21:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren!</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:26.120 --> 00:21:28.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We just wanted
to say thank you.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:28.580 --> 00:21:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We may not have been
fully prepared</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:30.370 --> 00:21:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this time around,
but we have three years</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:32.420 --> 00:21:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to train for the next one.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:33.840 --> 00:21:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. Good to hear.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:36.460 --> 00:21:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the fun.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Safe travels.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:39.300 --> 00:21:40.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I'll see you later.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:42.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
Right. See you!</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:42.380 --> 00:21:49.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:53.900 --> 00:21:56.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You kept that farewell
rather short and simple,</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:56.730 --> 00:21:58.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just like you did with Sein.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:58.730 --> 00:21:59.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] And with Kraft.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:22:00.860 --> 00:22:07.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000441
00:22:11.160 --> 00:22:12.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It's funny, Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:15.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You always bid
such quick goodbyes.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:22:15.920 --> 00:22:17.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's strange?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:22:17.420 --> 00:22:19.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Eh, it's more like
a break in character.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:22:20.130 --> 00:22:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It may have just
been a side job,</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:24.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we spent two weeks
traveling with him.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] Think of all
the laughs we shared.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:26.640 --> 00:22:28.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We drank with the fellow
practically every night.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:28.810 --> 00:22:31.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FRIEREN] You corrupt priest.
-[chuckles] You have a point.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:32.850 --> 00:22:34.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm not retiring soon,</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:34.730 --> 00:22:36.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I'm sure
our paths will cross</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:36.190 --> 00:22:37.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>somewhere down the line.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:38.900 --> 00:22:40.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
a tearful farewell</b></Default>

c0000454
00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:41.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would suit us anyway.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:22:47.120 --> 00:22:48.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And besides,</b></Default>

c0000456
00:22:48.700 --> 00:22:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would be embarrassing
when we met again.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:24:04.150 --> 00:24:05.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000458
00:24:06.280 --> 00:24:08.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be embarrassing
when we met again.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:24:09.490 --> 00:24:10.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Huh?
[FERN] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000460
00:24:10.660 --> 00:24:12.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] What is that
supposed to mean?</b></Default>

